summary: An ordinance relating to zoning, establishing Use, Area and Height Districts on a portion of Lot 1, Block 1, Assessor's Plat of Endolynd Addition, annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinance No. 79226 on January 1, 1951, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new sections numbered 2-277, 17-224 and 10-20, respectively.
